data.description: Save money by assuming the seller's loan on this hidden gem in Innerarity Point! Only 5 minutes away from Perdido Key, with no H.O.A. this house is off the beaten path yet close to everything you would want with N.A.S. just 15 minutes away, shopping and restaurants right down the street and Innerarity Park, Galvez Boat Ramp and Hub Stacey's just a short walk away! With 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms this house includes 2 master suites which make it a great family home or vacation home. On the ground floor is one of the master suites and there are two large living areas, separated by the galley kitchen and dining room, which are surrounded with windows that bring in all the natural light! Upstairs you will find the other master suite with a large walk-in closet to the left and two guest rooms and bathroom to the right. As you walk out to the back yard you will find a big wrap around deck that leads you down to a cozy, shaded, paved area with a nice stone firepit! There is also a small shed for your yard tools and the fence has a double gate where you could pull in a car or boat. The roof was replaced after hurricane Sally and the sellers have made several upgrades such as new interior and exterior paint, new shiplap ceilings in the bathrooms, new tile floors in bathrooms, new vanity in upstairs bathroom, and new countertops in the kitchen.
